MI)\n****\t\tBaseplate = Node for studying current induced \n****\t\t\t\t\tthrough heatsink into grounding system\n*********************************************************************\n****\tParameter Definitions:\n****\t\tRp   = Inductor parallel res (Ω)\n****\t\t\t\tlow pass filter on ringing\n****\t\t\t\t100 (default) good balance of bandwidth and sim-time\n****\t\t\t\t1m   removes impact of packaging but greatly improves sim time\n*********************************************************************\n.SUBCKT ECB4R3M12YM3 DC+1 DC+2 DC+3 DC-1 DC-2 DC-3 U V W G1 G2 G3 G4 G5 G6 K1 K2 K3 K4 K5 K6 TjQ1 TjQ2 TjQ3 TjQ4 TjQ5 TjQ6 TcQ1 TcQ2 TcQ3 TcQ4 TcQ5 TcQ6\n\n\n* Rp:parasitic inductance bypass. Set to 1m for increased speed, but less accuracy\n.param Rp=10\n\n* 1Meg resistances allow sim to run with Gate/Kelvins left open\nRgk1 G1 K1 1Meg\nRgk2 G2 K2 1Meg\nRgk3 G3 K3 1Meg\nRgk4 G4 K4 1Meg\nRgk5 G5 K5 1Meg\nRgk6 G6 K6 1Meg\n*** SiC MOSFETS ***\n* High Side *\nXDie_Electrical_Q1 DQ1 GQ1 SQ1 TjQ1 IQ1 Mosfet\nXDie_Electrical_Q3 DQ3 GQ3 SQ3 TjQ3 IQ3 Mosfet\nXDie_Electrical_Q5 DQ5 GQ5 SQ5 TjQ5 IQ5 Mosfet\n\n* Low Side *\nXDie_Electrical_Q2 SQ1 GQ2 SQ2 TjQ2 IQ2 Mosfet\nXDie_Electrical_Q4 SQ3 GQ4 SQ4 TjQ4 IQ4 Mosfet\nXDie_Electrical_Q6 SQ5 GQ6 SQ6 TjQ6 IQ6 Mosfet\n\n*** Thermal Networks ***\n* High Side *\nXDie_Thermal_Q1 TjQ1 TcQ1 DQ1 SQ1 IQ1 Thermal_Network PARAMS: Ct1=3.14m Ct2=52.30m Ct3=425.78m Ct4=5.10 Rt1=1.06m Rt2=8.20m Rt3=41.35m Rt4=50.39m\nXDie_Thermal_Q3 TjQ3 TcQ3 DQ3 SQ3 IQ3 Thermal_Network PARAMS: Ct1=3.14m Ct2=52.30m Ct3=425.78m Ct4=5.10 Rt1=1.06m Rt2=8.20m Rt3=41.35m Rt4=50.39m\nXDie_Thermal_Q5 TjQ5 TcQ5 DQ5 SQ5 IQ5 Thermal_Network PARAMS: Ct1=3.14m Ct2=52.30m Ct3=425.78m Ct4=5.10 Rt1=1.06m Rt2=8.20m Rt3=41.35m Rt4=50.39m\n* Low Side *\nXDie_Thermal_Q2 TjQ2 TcQ2 SQ1 SQ2 IQ2 Thermal_Network PARAMS: Ct1=3.14m Ct2=52.30m Ct3=425.78m Ct4=5.10 Rt1=1.06m Rt2=8.20m Rt3=41.35m Rt4=50.39m\nXDie_Thermal_Q4 TjQ4 TcQ4 SQ3 SQ4 IQ4 Thermal_Network PARAMS: Ct1=3.14m Ct2=52.30m Ct3=425.78m Ct4=5.10 Rt1=1.06m Rt2=8.20m Rt3=41.35m Rt4=50.39m\nXDie_Thermal_Q6 TjQ6 TcQ6 SQ5 SQ6 IQ6 Thermal_Network PARAMS: Ct1=3.14m Ct2=52.30m Ct3=425.78m Ct4=5.10 Rt1=1.06m Rt2=8.20m Rt3=41.35m Rt4=50.39m\n\n*** Baseplate Capacitance [COMMENTED: uncomment and add a baseplate pin if desired!] ***\n*Cu1g DQ1 Baseplate 243.12p\n*Cu3g DQ3 Baseplate 243.12p\n*Ca1g SQ1 Baseplate 262.66p\n*Ca2g SQ3 Baseplate 262.66p\n*Ca3g SQ5 Baseplate 262.66p\n*Cl1g SQ2 Baseplate 73.08p\n*Cl2g SQ4 Baseplate 73.08p\n*Cl3g SQ6 Baseplate 73.08p\n\n*** Parasitic Parameters ***\nLP1D DC+1 DC+1intDQ1 7.87n\nRsP1D DC+1intDQ1 DQ1 600.00u\nRpP1D DC+1 DQ1 {Rp}\nLP2D DC+2 DC+2intDQ3 7.87n\nRsP2D DC+2intDQ3 DQ3 600.00u\nRpP2D DC+2 DQ3 {Rp}\nLP3D DC+3 DC+3intDQ5 7.87n\nRsP3D DC+3intDQ5 DQ5 600.00u\nRpP3D DC+3 DQ5 {Rp}\n\n\nLP1P SQ1 SQ1intU 53.20n\nRsP1P SQ1intU U 600.00u\nRpP1P SQ1 U {Rp}\nLP2P SQ3 SQ3intV 53.20n\nRsP2P SQ3intV V 600.00u\nRpP2P SQ3 V {Rp}\nLP3P SQ5 SQ5intW 53.20n\nRsP3P SQ5intW W 600.00u\nRpP3P SQ5 W {Rp}\n\nLP1S SQ2 SQ2intDC-1 53.20n\nRsP1S SQ2intDC-1 DC-1 600.00u\nRpP1S SQ2 DC-1 {Rp}\nLP2S SQ4 SQ4intDC-2 53.20n\nRsP2S SQ4intDC-2 DC-2 600.00u\nRpP2S SQ4 DC-2 {Rp}\nLP3S SQ6 SQ6intDC-3 53.20n\nRsP3S SQ6intDC-3 DC-3 600.00u\nRpP3S SQ6 DC-3 {Rp}\n\nLQ1G G1 G1intGQ1 9.96n\nRsQ1G G1intGQ1 GQ1 1.01\nLQ2G G2 G2intGQ2 5.96n\nRsQ2G G2intGQ2 GQ2 1.01\nLQ3G G3 G3intGQ3 9.96n\nRsQ3G G3intGQ3 GQ3 1.01\nLQ4G G4 G4intGQ4 5.96n\nRsQ4G G4intGQ4 GQ4 1.01\nLQ5G G5 G5intGQ5 9.96n\nRsQ5G G5intGQ5 GQ5 1.01\nLQ6G G6 G6intGQ6 5.96n\nRsQ6G G6intGQ6 GQ6 1.01\n\nLQ1K K1 K1intSQ1 9.96n\nRsQ1K K1intSQ1 SQ1 1.01\nLQ2K K2 K2intSQ2 5.96n\nRsQ2K K2intSQ2 SQ2 1.01\nLQ3K K3 K3intSQ3 9.96n\nRsQ3K K3intSQ3 SQ3 1.01\nLQ4K K4 K4intSQ4 5.96n\nRsQ4K K4intSQ4 SQ4 1.01\nLQ5K K5 K5intSQ5 9.96n\nRsQ5K K5intSQ5 SQ5 1.01\nLQ6K K6 K6intSQ6 5.96n\nRsQ6K K6intSQ6 SQ6 1.01\n\n.ENDS ECB4R3M12YM3\n\n.SUBCKT Thermal_Network Tj Tc Vp Vn Vi PARAMS: Ct1=1 Ct2=1 Ct3=1 Ct4=1 Rt1=1 Rt2=1 Rt3=1 Rt4=1\nGPwr 0 Tj Value {abs(V(Vp,Vn)*(V(